 Religion? Social Indicators Research, 101: 1-15.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote>转载自：<a href="http://column.caijing.com.cn/2012-09-26/112155192.html" target="_blank">宗教会让你更幸福吗？</a></blockquote>', '宗教会让你更幸福吗？', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '275-revision-2', '', '', '2012-09-26 17:32:27', '2012-09-26 09:32:27', '', 275, 'http://uxfeel.com/?p=277', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
