(374, 3, '2012-09-26 00:38:41', '2012-09-25 16:38:41', '2010 年是 <a href="http://www.mangguo.org/tag/html5">HTML5</a> 如火如荼的一年，浏览器行业给力的发展，技术的更新，无疑给 Web 带来了更为宽阔的未来。这里是来自<a href="http://webdesignledger.com/" target="_blank">Web Design Ledger</a> 网站的 <a href="http://www.mangguo.org/35-inspiring-examples-of-websites-using-html5">35 款应用 HTML5 的网站案例</a>，值得学习和收藏。\r\n<h2><a href="http://michaelacevedo.com/" target="_blank">Michael Acevedo</a></h2>\r\n<a href="http://michaelacevedo.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/html5sites01.jpg" alt="html5sites01" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="http://html5.iaraby.com/" target="_blank">html5.iaraby.com</a></h2>\r\n<a href="http://html5.iaraby.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/html5sites02.jpg" alt="html5sites02" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="http://vtech.trefl.com/" target="_blank">vtech</a></h2>\r\n<a href="http://vtech.trefl.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/html5sites03.jpg" alt="html5sites03" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="http://benthebodyguard.com/index-b.php" target="_blank">Ben the Bodyguard</a></h2>\r\n<a href="http://benthebodyguard.com/index-b.php" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/html5sites04.jpg" alt="html5sites04" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.ostragoth.co.uk/" target="_blank">Ostragoth Publishing</a></h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.ostragoth.co.uk/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/html5sites05.jpg" alt="html5sites05" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="http://wantist.com/" target="_blank">Wantist</a></h2>\r\n<a href="http://wantist.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/html5sites06.jpg" alt="html5sites06" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.petrosalema.com/_/" target="_blank">Petro Salema</a></h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.petrosalema.com/_/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-c