ket</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://studioracket.org/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/24-14_studio_racket.jpg" alt="Studio Racket" width="550" height="153" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>14. <a href="http://lauraalter.com/blog" target="_blank">Laura Alter</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://lauraalter.com/blog" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/24-15_laura_alter.jpg" alt="Laura Alter" width="550" height="213" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>15. <a href="http://www.sohtanaka.com/" target="_blank">Soh Tanaka</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sohtanaka.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/24-16_sohtanaka.jpg" alt="Soh Tanaka" width="550" height="207" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>16. <a href="http://www.davidhellmann.com/" target="_blank">David Hellmann</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.davidhellmann.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/24-17_david_hellmann.jpg" alt="David Hellmann" width="550" height="150" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>17. <a href="http://kailoon.com/" target="_blank">Kailoon</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://kailoon.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/24-18_kailoon.jpg" alt="Kailoon" width="550" height="200" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>18. <a href="http://samrayner.com/" target="_blank">Sam Rayner</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://samrayner.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/24-19_sam_rayner.jpg" alt="Sam Rayner" width="550" height="217" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>19. <a href="http://www.catydesign-studio.com/" target="_blank">Caty Design Studio</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.catydesign-studio.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.mangguo.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/24-20_caty_design_studio.jpg" alt="Caty Design Studio" width="550" height="181" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>20. <a href="http://www.prod